WEBVTT

00:00.288 --> 00:02.009
He's looking for you,
Tom

00:02.033 --> 00:03.985
Previously on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:04.009 --> 00:05.639
We're gonna need
all the allies we can get.

00:05.663 --> 00:07.984
Those bastards aren't gonna quit
until they find us, again.

00:08.007 --> 00:09.051
You ever taken one down?

00:09.075 --> 00:10.248
I have.

00:10.390 --> 00:13.108
I am the only shot you got
to survive.

00:13.530 --> 00:15.172
Why would the Espheni
leave this place alone?

00:15.287 --> 00:17.381
How the hell
did this happen?

00:18.203 --> 00:19.656
Your daughter's
very special.

00:20.227 --> 00:22.520
shouldn't we give her the chance
to prove she's on our side --

00:22.544 --> 00:23.907
that she's still
one of us?

00:23.931 --> 00:25.619
Worst-case scenario,
what happens?

00:25.643 --> 00:26.745
Worst-case...

00:26.769 --> 00:28.288
She kills you all.

