01:48.906 --> 01:52.508
Lexi?
Are you all right?

01:52.543 --> 01:54.877
Her eyes.

01:54.912 --> 01:57.980
What happened
to her eyes?

01:59.183 --> 02:01.951
Lexi?!
Lexi! Oh!

02:01.985 --> 02:05.087
Lexi?

02:05.122 --> 02:07.190
Honey?

02:07.257 --> 02:08.958
Lexi?

02:12.896 --> 02:14.397
Mom?

02:14.431 --> 02:17.533
I'm here.
We're both here.

02:17.568 --> 02:19.769
It's me.

02:19.803 --> 02:21.938
Tom Mason?

02:21.972 --> 02:23.139
You remember.

02:23.173 --> 02:25.374
I'm your father.

02:28.345 --> 02:30.313
Lexi!

02:34.751 --> 02:35.985
Is there anything
you need?

02:37.421 --> 02:39.922
We're so glad you're all right,
that you're back with us.

02:42.993 --> 02:44.260
I have to go.
Go, Lexi?

02:44.294 --> 02:45.995
No,
you can't go anywhere

02:46.029 --> 02:48.297
until I've had a chance to calm
everybody down out there.

02:48.365 --> 02:51.501
I could hear them.
Their fear, their hatred.

02:51.535 --> 02:53.903
They wanted to hurt me.
No.

02:53.937 --> 02:55.738
We didn't know what was
going on in there.

02:55.772 --> 02:58.274
People were afraid that you
were gonna come out...

02:58.308 --> 02:59.876
different, dangerous.

02:59.910 --> 03:01.544
The faithful never believed
that, not for a second.

03:01.578 --> 03:03.045
I am different.

03:03.080 --> 03:04.480
I tried to help those
who lived here

03:04.481 --> 03:06.349
to make peace
with their enemies,

03:06.383 --> 03:08.150
but I see now
there's no use.

03:08.185 --> 03:11.287
Humans cannot let go
of their warlike ways.

03:11.321 --> 03:13.456
So it's time for me
to leave here.

03:13.490 --> 03:15.858
I don't understand.

03:15.893 --> 03:18.227
You spoke to me
when you were in the cocoon.

03:18.262 --> 03:20.229
You said you would
always need your family.

03:20.264 --> 03:23.499
You misunderstood.
Not this family.

03:25.135 --> 03:27.103
Your hearts are filled
with violence.

03:27.137 --> 03:28.838
I try to show you
another path,

03:28.872 --> 03:31.774
but you don't have
the courage to change.

03:31.808 --> 03:33.943
There's nothing more
I can do.

03:33.977 --> 03:35.411
For any of you.

03:35.445 --> 03:37.113
Wait, please.

03:37.180 --> 03:41.117
Lexi...I never gave up
on the dream.

03:41.184 --> 03:44.320
For that, I will always be
grateful to you, Lourdes.

03:44.354 --> 03:46.522
Lexi, you're right.
They are afraid of you.

03:46.557 --> 03:48.190
They may try to hurt you.
Let them try.

03:49.993 --> 03:51.260
Lexi.
Lexi.

03:55.399 --> 03:58.935
Lexi, wait!

03:58.969 --> 04:00.436
Lexi!

04:01.838 --> 04:04.807
Don't take another step.
I mean it.

04:04.841 --> 04:06.809
Pope, trust me.
Don't do it.

04:06.843 --> 04:08.511
If she wanted to hurt us,
she would have done it by now.

04:08.545 --> 04:11.414
At every step, you people
respond with violence.

04:11.448 --> 04:13.015
You Masons
are always so damn eager

04:13.050 --> 04:14.450
to make excuses
for one of your own.

04:14.451 --> 04:16.786
I'm leaving.
Don't try to stop me.

04:16.853 --> 04:20.322
Lexi, wait.
Please, take me with you.

04:20.357 --> 04:23.259
Before I met you,
I'd lost everything.

04:23.293 --> 04:25.127
I-I didn't know
who I was anymore,

04:25.162 --> 04:27.863
and you saved me.

04:27.898 --> 04:29.899
You're in so much pain.

04:29.933 --> 04:31.000
These last few months,

04:31.034 --> 04:32.969
you've given me a reason
to go on.

04:33.003 --> 04:36.439
Without you,
I can't...

04:36.473 --> 04:40.176
I won't.
I'm afraid.

04:40.243 --> 04:42.712
Poor Lourdes.

04:42.779 --> 04:44.981
Would you like me
to set you free?

04:45.015 --> 04:46.849
Oh, thank you, Lexi.

04:46.883 --> 04:49.085
You know I'll always
be beside you.

04:49.119 --> 04:52.221
Yes. Always in my heart,
Lourdes.

04:55.292 --> 04:57.426
Breathe deeply.

05:02.532 --> 05:06.235
Wait. What are you --
what are you doing?

05:06.269 --> 05:07.370
Don't be scared.

05:07.404 --> 05:09.905
Lexi! Lexi, stop it!
Lexi!

05:14.811 --> 05:17.146
I'm not doing this!

05:17.180 --> 05:18.481
Just let go.

05:18.515 --> 05:21.784
I'm not ready.

05:21.818 --> 05:23.185
You're free.

05:27.290 --> 05:30.359
Somebody take a shot!
Aah!

05:31.061 --> 05:33.462
- Lourdes! Lourdes!
- Lourdes!

05:33.497 --> 05:35.865
Where did she go?!

05:45.308 --> 05:47.176
She's gone.

